==German==
===Etymology===
From ''Austrien'', "Eastern Empire" as opposed to ''Neustrien'' (ne=not Austrien), "Western Empire".
See [[w:Neustria|Wikipedia:Neustrien]], [[w:Austrasia|Wikipedia:Austrien]]. 
===Proper Noun===
'''Österreich''' ''n''
# [[Austria]]

